OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOutbreaks of locally heavy
OL,6,Fshowery rain at first. This rain will
OL,7,Fclear to bright spells and scattered
OL,8,Fshowers before the afternoon. Much of
OL,9,Fthe afternoon stays cloudy with
OL,10,Foccasional showers.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FBright or clear spells with
OL,13,Fshowery rain at first becoming cloudy
OL,14,Fwith outbreaks of rain, some heavy,
OL,15,Ffrom just after midnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,18,Foccasionally heavy rain becoming drier
OL,19,Fwith bright spells and showers from
OL,20,Fthe mid-afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
