OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRain
OL,6,Fclears north early Saturday morning to
OL,7,Fleave the day and Sunday dry and
OL,8,Fbright. A band of cloud and outbreaks
OL,9,Fof rain, pass east early Monday
OL,10,Fmorning.
